OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely dry across Wales today
OL,6,Fwith some early mist patches. Sunny
OL,7,Fspells at first, but clouding over a
OL,8,Flittle during the afternoon, with a
OL,9,Fsmall chance of a few showers. Less
OL,10,Fwindy than Saturday.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FAny showers easing to leave a
OL,13,Fdry end to the day with some late
OL,14,Fsunny spells. A few showers possible
OL,15,Fin the south in the early hours.
OL,16,FTurning chilly overnight.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FA bright start for many, but
OL,19,Fclouding over through the day as
OL,20,Fshowery outbreaks of rain spread north
OL,21,Fduring the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
